==Japanese== '''Ōmiwa Shrine''' (大神神社、おおみわじんじゃ、おおがじんじゃ) refers to Shinto shrines with the name "大神".
==Kantō Region== * {{ill|Ōmiwa Shrine (Tochigi, Tochigi)|ja|大神神社 (栃木市)|12=draft|12=draft}} ({{ill|Tochigi Prefecture|ja|栃木県|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|Tochigi|ja|栃木市|12=draft|12=draft}}) – A {{ill|Shikinai-sha|ja|式内社|1=Shikinaisha|12=draft|12=draft}} of {{ill|Tsuga District (Shimotsuke Province)|ja|都賀郡|12=draft|12=draft}} in {{ill|Shimotsuke Province|ja|下野国|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Ōmiwa Shrine (Ōtawara)|ja|大神神社（大田原市）|12=draft|12=draft}} (Tochigi Prefecture, {{ill|Ōtawara|ja|大田原市|12=draft|12=draft}})
==Chūbu Region== * {{ill|Ōmiwa Shrine (Ichinomiya)|ja|大神神社 (一宮市)|12=draft|12=draft}} ({{ill|Aichi Prefecture|ja|愛知県|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|Ichinomiya, Aichi|ja|一宮市|12=draft|12=draft}} Hanaike) – A {{ill|Shikinai-sha|ja|式内社|1=Shikinaisha|12=draft|12=draft}} of {{ill|Nakajima District (Owari Province)|ja|中島郡|12=draft|12=draft}} in {{ill|Owari Province|ja|尾張国|12=draft|12=draft}}, possibly considered the {{ill|Ichinomiya|ja|一宮|12=draft|12=draft}} of Owari. * {{ill|Ōmiwa Shrine (Ichinomiya, Yamatocho Oho)|ja|大神神社 (一宮市大和町於保)|12=draft|12=draft}} (Ichinomiya, Aichi, Yamatocho Oho) * {{ill|Ōmiwa Shrine (Ichinomiya, Yamatocho Miyaji)|ja|大神神社 (一宮市大和町宮地)|12=draft|12=draft}} (Ichinomiya, Aichi, Yamatocho Miyaji) * {{ill|Ōmiwa Shrine (Ōgaki)|ja|大神神社 (大垣市)|12=draft|12=draft}} ({{ill|Gifu Prefecture|ja|岐阜県|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|Ōgaki|ja|大垣市|12=draft|12=draft}}) – A Shikinai-sha of {{ill|Tage District (Mino Province)|ja|多芸郡|12=draft|12=draft}} in {{ill|Mino Province|ja|美濃国|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Ōmiwa Shrine (Ikeda, Gifu)|ja|大神神社 (池田町)|12=draft|12=draft}} (Gifu Prefecture, {{ill|Ikeda, Gifu|ja|池田町|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Ibi District, Gifu|ja|揖斐郡|12=draft|12=draft}}) * {{ill|Ōmiwa Shrine (Iga)|ja|大神神社 (伊賀市)|12=draft|12=draft}} ({{ill|Mie Prefecture|ja|三重県|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|Iga, Mie|ja|伊賀市|12=draft|12=draft}}) * {{ill|Ninomiya Shrine (Kosai)|ja|二宮神社|12=draft|12=draft}} ({{ill|Shizuoka Prefecture|ja|静岡県|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|Kosai, Shizuoka|ja|湖西市|12=draft|12=draft}}) – Identified with an Ōmiwa Shrine.
==Kinki Region== * {{ill|Ōmiwa Shrine (Nagahama)|ja|大神神社 (長浜市)|12=draft|12=draft}} ({{ill|Shiga Prefecture|ja|滋賀県|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|Nagahama|ja|長浜市|12=draft|12=draft}}) * {{ill|Ōmiwa Shrine|ja|大神神社|12=draft|12=draft}} ({{ill|Sakurai, Nara|ja|桜井市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Nara Prefecture|ja|奈良県|12=draft|12=draft}}) – A {{ill|Shikinai-sha|ja|式内社|1=Shikinaisha|12=draft|12=draft}} of {{ill|Shikage District|ja|式上郡|12=draft|12=draft}} in {{ill|Yamato Province|ja|大和国|12=draft|12=draft}} ({{ill|Myōjin Taisha|ja|名神大社|12=draft|12=draft}}), historically known as "Ōmiwa Ōmononushi Jinja," a former {{ill|Kanpei-taisha|ja|官幣大社|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Ōmiwa Shrine (Yamatokoriyama)|ja|大神神社 (大和郡山市)|12=draft|12=draft}} (Nara Prefecture, {{ill|Yamatokoriyama|ja|大和郡山市|12=draft|12=draft}}) * {{ill|Ōmiwa Shrine (Nara City)|ja|大神神社 (奈良市)|12=draft|12=draft}} (Nara Prefecture, {{ill|Nara|ja|奈良市|12=draft|12=draft}}) * {{ill|Daijingūsha|ja|大神宮社|12=draft|12=draft}} ({{ill|Minamiyamashiro|ja|南山城村|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Kyoto Prefecture|ja|京都府|12=draft|12=draft}})
==Chūgoku Region== * {{ill|Ōmiwa Shrine (Okayama)|ja|大神神社 (岡山市)|12=draft|12=draft}} ({{ill|Okayama|ja|岡山市|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|Naka-ku, Okayama|ja|中区|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Okayama Prefecture|ja|岡山県|12=draft|12=draft}}) – A Shikinai-sha of {{ill|Jōtō District (Bizen Province)|ja|上道郡|12=draft|12=draft}} in {{ill|Bizen Province|ja|備前国|12=draft|12=draft}}.
==Kyushu Region== * {{ill|Ōmiwa Shrine (Takami-dai, Fukuoka)|ja|大神神社|12=draft|12=draft}} ({{ill|Fukuoka|ja|福岡市|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|Higashi-ku, Fukuoka|ja|東区|12=draft|12=draft}} Takami-dai) * {{ill|Ōmiwa Shrine (Wajirogaoka, Fukuoka)|ja|大神神社|12=draft|12=draft}} (Fukuoka City, Higashi-ku, Wajirogaoka)
==See Also== * {{ill|Miwa Shrine (disambiguation)|ja|三輪神社 (曖昧さ回避)|12=draft|12=draft}} * {{ill|Miwa Shrine|ja|美和神社 (曖昧さ回避)|12=draft|12=draft}} * {{ill|Sanwa Shrine|ja|三和神社|12=draft|12=draft}} * {{ill|Mitsu Torii|ja|三ツ鳥居|12=draft|12=draft}} * {{ill|Mihashira Torii|ja|三柱鳥居|12=draft|12=draft}}
